      <div class="figure">
        <img src="/manuals/milwaukee-2535-20/p02_00.png" alt="Wiring diagram for the Milwaukee 2535-20 sander showing battery connector, terminal block, motor, LED work light, speed selector, main PCBA, fuse, light pipe PCB, and on-off switch, with accessory part list" />
